# Genetic

This algorithm will simulate multiple children using and sharing the same DNA from his parent.

## Training example

#### Client settings
```
34 characters to find
10 childrens per generation
2000 mutations maximum per child
```

#### Trainig output

367-344878334

;generation
36

;total dna mutations
48783
